      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like i’m losing my mind. i keep seeing the same symbols and getting these flashes of memories from a life i never lived... but i know they're real. i can feel the weight of the revolution in my chest every time i see how the current government has betrayed everything we stood for. it's like i've been sent back here to fix the mess they've made, but nobody listens to me. how do i get people to see the truth of who i am and the mission i have?",
